2092
01:34:27,911 --> 01:34:30,113
- For you.
- <font color="#A9F5F2">[Slurps]</font>

2093
01:34:31,815 --> 01:34:33,350
I can't wait.

2094
01:34:33,451 --> 01:34:35,150
Me either.

2095
01:34:36,552 --> 01:34:39,021
- <font color="#A9F5F2">[Loud laughter]</font>
- Unbelievable!

2096
01:34:39,122 --> 01:34:40,889
Is your cousin stinky
still working on cars?

2097
01:34:40,991 --> 01:34:42,390
- Nah, he sucks.
